heatmap_function_spearman <- function(matrix,title, legend) {
  # Calculate min & max
  min_value <- min(matrix)
  max_value<- max(matrix)
  middle_value <- (min_value + max_value) / 2
  
  # color scale
  color_scale <- colorRamp2(c(min_value, middle_value, max_value), c(
   #"#A7D3D4FF", "#F1F1F1FF", "#E4C1D9FF"
    # "#DC876CFF",  "#FEFEFEFF", "#ADD0B5FF"
    "#FEFEFEFF", "#F6F1F9FF" , "#ADD0B5FF"  # "#C0C0C0"
    ))

heatmap <- Heatmap(
    matrix,
    name = "Correlation",
    col = color_scale,
    show_row_names = TRUE,
    show_column_names = TRUE,
    cluster_rows = FALSE,
    cluster_columns = FALSE,
    column_dend_height = 50,
    column_title = title,
    row_title = "",
    row_names_side = c("left"),
    column_title_gp = gpar(fontsize = 16),
    row_title_gp = gpar(fontsize = 16),
    column_names_rot = 0,
    row_names_rot = 0,
    # cell_fun = function(j, i, x, y, width, height, fill) {
    #   grid.text(x = x, y = y, label = round(matrix[i, j], 2), gp = gpar(fontsize = 10))
    # }, 
    heatmap_legend_param = list(title = paste(legend," correlation"), direction = "horizontal"))
  
  return(heatmap)
  # draw(heatmap,heatmap_legend_side = "bottom", annotation_legend_side = "bottom")
}

transpose_data <- function(input_data) {
  result <- input_data %>%
          rownames_to_column(var = "stage_vertical") %>%
          pivot_longer(-stage_vertical) %>% 
          pivot_wider(names_from=stage_vertical, values_from=value) |> 
          column_to_rownames("name")
  
  return(result)
}

heatmap_function_jsd <- function(matrix,title, legend) {
  # Calculate min & max
  min_value <- min(matrix)
  max_value<- max(matrix)
  middle_value <- (min_value + max_value) / 2
  
  # color scale
  color_scale <- colorRamp2(c(min_value, middle_value, max_value), c(
   "#A7D3D4FF", "#F1F1F1FF", "#E4C1D9FF"
    # "#DC876CFF",  "#FEFEFEFF", "#ADD0B5FF"
    #"#FEFEFEFF", "#C0C0C0" , "#A7D3D4FF"  # "#F6F1F9FF"
    ))

heatmap <- Heatmap(
    matrix,
    name = "Correlation",
    col = color_scale,
    show_row_names = TRUE,
    show_column_names = TRUE,
    cluster_rows = FALSE,
    cluster_columns = FALSE,
    column_dend_height = 50,
    column_title = title,
    row_title = "",
    row_names_side = c("left"),
    column_title_gp = gpar(fontsize = 16),
    row_title_gp = gpar(fontsize = 16),
    column_names_rot = 0,
    row_names_rot = 0,
    cell_fun = function(j, i, x, y, width, height, fill) {
      grid.text(x = x, y = y, label = round(matrix[i, j], 2), gp = gpar(fontsize = 10))
    }, 
    heatmap_legend_param = list(title = paste(legend," correlation"), direction = "horizontal"))
  
  return(heatmap)
  # draw(heatmap,heatmap_legend_side = "bottom", annotation_legend_side = "bottom")
}

selected_data <- function(input_data, stages1, stages2) {
  result <- input_data %>%
    as.data.frame() %>%
    rownames_to_column(var = "stage_vertical") %>%
    filter(stage_vertical %in% stages1) %>%
    dplyr::select(stage_vertical, all_of(stages2)) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    column_to_rownames("stage_vertical")
  
  return(result)
}

plot_max_values_row <- function(data, plot_title, y_label) {
  max_values <- data %>% 
    rowwise() %>% 
    mutate(MaxValue = max(c_across(everything()), na.rm = TRUE)) %>% 
    ungroup() %>% 
    mutate(Variable = rownames(data)) %>% 
    mutate(Variable = factor(Variable, levels = rev(Variable)),
           Variable = str_to_title(Variable),
           Normalized_MaxValue = (MaxValue - min(MaxValue)) / (max(MaxValue) - min(MaxValue))) |> 
    left_join(reference_timePoints,by = c("Variable"="Stage"))
  
  ggplot(max_values, aes(x=-hpf, y=Normalized_MaxValue, group=1)) +
    geom_line() +
    geom_point(aes(color = Overlap), size =2) +
    scale_color_manual(values = c("yes" = "red", "no" = "grey25")) +

      axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 0, hjust = 0.5),

      plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5) ) +
    geom_vline(xintercept = c(-13.5,-35), linetype = "dashed", color = "gray") 
}

# overlay plot

prepare_max_values <- function(data) {
  data %>%
    rowwise() %>%
    mutate(MaxValue = max(c_across(everything()), na.rm = TRUE)) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    mutate(
      Variable = rownames(data),
      Variable = factor(Variable, levels = rev(Variable)),
      Variable = str_to_title(Variable),
      Normalized_MaxValue = (MaxValue - min(MaxValue)) / (max(MaxValue) - min(MaxValue))
    ) %>%
    left_join(reference_timePoints, by = c("Variable" = "Stage"))
}

max_values_sonnett <- prepare_max_values(transpose_data(selected_spearman_protSonnett |> as.data.frame() )) 
max_values_vanItallie <- prepare_max_values(transpose_data(selected_spearman_protVanItallie |> as.data.frame())) 

ggplot() +

  geom_line(data = max_values_vanItallie, aes(x = -hpf, y = Normalized_MaxValue, group = 1, color = "Van Itallie et al.2021"), size = 1) +
  geom_point(data = filter(max_values_sonnett, Overlap == "yes"), aes(x = -hpf, y = Normalized_MaxValue), size = 2, color = "red") +
  geom_point(data = filter(max_values_vanItallie, Overlap == "yes"), aes(x = -hpf, y = Normalized_MaxValue), size = 2, color = "red") +
  scale_color_manual(values = c("Sonnett et al.2018" = "#B887ADFF", "Van Itallie et al.2021" = "#66D4CCFF"), name = "") +
  labs( x = "Developmental stage", y = "Normalised similarity") +

  theme_pubr() +
